item.title: What If a Supervolcano Erupted Tomorrow?
item.dc:creator: Soham Mahajan
item.description: Supervolcanoes are one of nature’s most destructive forces, capable of reshaping entire continents. But what would actually happen if one erupted? From catastrophic climate effects to global chaos, explore the chilling scenarios that could unfold.
